flowchart TD
    START([Student opens Resume Enhancer]) --> WELCOME{Choose path}
    WELCOME -->|Build CV| FORMAT{Local or Global?}
    WELCOME -->|Analyze| UPLOAD[Upload PDF/DOCX]
    FORMAT --> FORM[Fill builder form]
    FORM --> PERSIST[Persist to localStorage]
    FORM --> EDITOR{Open Live Editor?}
    EDITOR -->|Yes| LIVE[Inline edit + AI rewrite]
    EDITOR -->|No| REVIEW[Review preview]
    LIVE --> EXPORT
    REVIEW --> EXPORT[POST /api/resume/generate]
    UPLOAD --> CONVERT[POST /api/resume/convert]
    CONVERT --> SCORE[Heuristic + AI analyze]
    SCORE --> AIEDIT[Optional AI edit]
    AIEDIT --> EXPORT
    EXPORT --> DOWNLOAD[PDF or DOCX download]
